== 目标与职能 ==
=== 目标 ===
'''文莱中央銀行'''之主要目标有四点{{refTag|1={{Cite web|url=http://www.ambd.gov.bn/about-ambd/objectives|title=Objectives of Autoriti Monetari Brunei Darussalam|accessdate=2014-07-06|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|trans_title=|format=|work=|publisher='''''Autoriti Monetari Brunei Darussalam'''''|pages=|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QoWZ7NHl?url=http://www.ambd.gov.bn/about-ambd/objectives|archivedate=2014-07-04|quote=The four main objectives of AMBD as prescribed under the Autoriti Monetari Brunei Darussalam Order, 2010 are as follows:-To achieve and maintain domestic price stability.To ensure the stability of the financial system, in particular by formulating financial regulations and prudential standards.To assist in the establishment and functioning of efficient payment systems and to oversee them; and.To foster and develop a sound and progressive financial services sector.|deadurl=yes}}}}{{refTag|name=nianbao2013|1=}}{{rp|xiii}}：
*保持以及维护国内[[物价|物价]]稳定； 
*通过制定[[金融|金融]]法规和[[审慎监管|审慎监管]]标准，确保金融体系的稳定；
*建立高效的支付系统，并监督其运作；
*培育和发展健全以及逐步发展的[[金融服务业|金融服务业]]；
=== 职能 ===
'''文莱中央銀行'''的职能为{{refTag|1={{Cite web|url=http://www.mof.gov.bn/index.php/component/content/article/18-bcmb/162-inroduction-bunei-currency-a-monetary-board |title=Function of Bunei Currency & Monetary Board |accessdate=2014-07-06 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |date= |year= |month= |trans_title=职能-文莱货币与金融委员会 |format= |work= |publisher='''''Ministry of Finance of Brunei''''' |pages= |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706032611/http://www.mof.gov.bn/index.php/component/content/article/18-bcmb/162-inroduction-bunei-currency-a-monetary-board |archivedate=2014-07-06 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}}}：
*1、印制[[文莱元|文莱元]][[纸币|纸币]]与铸造文莱元[[硬币|硬币]]；
*2、依照规定对[[文莱元|文莱元]]的发行、流通、回收等事务进行管理；
*3、为维持[[文莱元|文莱元]]的国际价值与足够的[[货币|货币]]供应备份，对[[外汇储备|外汇储备]]进行保管及监督；
*4、通过监测[[宏观经济|宏观经济]]指标的变化，来确保[[资金流通|资金流通]]保持在适当的水平，以促进[[货币|货币]]的稳定；
*5、代理[[财政部|财政部]]发行[[伊斯兰债券|伊斯兰债券]]；
*6、应[[财政部|财政部]]的要求，保管最小限度的国内银行[[存款准备金|存款准备金]]；
*7、与[[国际组织|国际组织]]保持信息交流与合作；

